</entry><entry thead="yes"><para>Purpose  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput><ref refid="classhelios_1_1ecs_1_1EntityRegistry" kindref="compound">helios.ecs.EntityRegistry</ref></computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Primary consumer of the lookup strategy concept  </para>
